39:44.267 --> 39:48.600
and an RCA 77 right there
for your voices,

39:48.667 --> 39:51.733
which I have determined,
after careful consideration,

39:51.800 --> 39:53.167
to be most effective

39:53.233 --> 39:56.533
if you sang into it
from a distance of exactly...

