-Six inches?
-Yes! Damn it!

40:01.967 --> 40:04.700
Six inches.

40:13.567 --> 40:16.267
What in the hell
is your problem?

40:16.333 --> 40:19.033
Oh, nothing, Marion,
I am peachy.

40:19.100 --> 40:20.900
These people
are customers, Sam.

40:20.967 --> 40:22.300
We need them to pay the bills.

40:22.367 --> 40:23.933
Oh, don't I know it.

40:24.000 --> 40:27.100
We record
"Anything, anywhere, anytime."

40:27.167 --> 40:30.767
Nothing too low or corny
or humiliating

40:30.833 --> 40:34.433
for old Sam Phillips.

40:34.500 --> 40:36.300
Sam, you need to
take a break for a second

40:36.367 --> 40:37.367
and go outside...

40:37.433 --> 40:39.700
Doc says I need electro-shock.

40:40.533 --> 40:42.100
No!

40:42.167 --> 40:44.067
You just need to
stop taking those pills.

40:44.133 --> 40:46.133
Hey, I got an idea.

40:46.200 --> 40:48.333
Instead of just funerals,

40:48.400 --> 40:50.700
why don't we set up
in the TB ward,

40:50.767 --> 40:53.900
so people can actually
hear their loved ones

40:53.967 --> 40:55.767
gurgling to death?

40:56.933 --> 40:59.200
Yeah. Yeah.

41:22.767 --> 41:23.767
Dad.

41:26.833 --> 41:27.933
Hey, tiger.

41:30.533 --> 41:32.967
