see the Chicks play

41:33.067 --> 41:34.233
at Russwood tonight.

41:39.167 --> 41:41.367
I'll get us tickets real soon.

41:43.867 --> 41:44.900
Wanna play catch?

41:49.567 --> 41:50.733
Hmm.

41:53.233 --> 41:55.433
Hmm. Nice catch, buddy.

41:56.700 --> 41:59.533
Daddy's not feeling
himself right now, baby.

41:59.600 --> 42:00.967
Why don't you go play outside

42:01.067 --> 42:02.100
and I'll let you know
when supper's ready?

42:02.167 --> 42:03.833
-Okay.
-Okay.

42:12.367 --> 42:13.867
I know...

42:15.500 --> 42:17.733
I'm no good
to anyone like this.

42:20.100 --> 42:22.633
Becks, I'm going down
that rabbit hole again.

42:25.067 --> 42:26.567
You should call Dr. Walden.

42:27.500 --> 42:29.733
-Sam...
-It's okay.

42:32.600 --> 42:34.400
I'm going to be all right.

